name: Soulpurger's Crown
flavor: Nearly overwhelmed by the corrupted, they fell into formation around the priests, deep in prayer...

name: Soulpurger's Garment
flavor: ...Zealously, they chanted, as light began to pierce the blackened sky, clearing the unnatural darkness around them...

name: Soulpurger's Blade
flavor: ...Night turned into day as hundreds of screams echoed in the light; their souls torn from corrupted husks. They had been purged.

name: Soulpurger's Aegis
flavor: ...The Templars' weapons now brimmed with light and holy energy, and upon striking their foes, enormous blasts of pure light erupted...

name: Thundering Will
flavor: Alone, she stood among the bodies of her fallen sisters, surrounded by unholy demons...

name: Thundering Bastion
flavor: ...Facing a certain defeat, she was left with only one option, and raised her blade towards the sky...

name: Thundering Charge
flavor: ...Empowered, she shouted: Rise, sisters, and purge this land with righteous thunder!

name: Thundering Guard
flavor: ...Thunder rumbled in the skies above, and cracked with a deafening boom as it struck her raised blade...

name: Skysoul Helmet
flavor: Suddenly, the Sky Lords, who had sailed on the clouds for generations, were cast to the ground...

name: Skysoul Armor
flavor: ...The great Dragons of the sky all rose together, soaring far above the highest clouds...

name: Skysoul Pounders
flavor: ...And one day, they shall return.

name: Skysoul Claws
flavor: ..Away into oblivion. Quickly, quietly, and without warning, they all disappeared...

name: Dragonfire Claws
flavor: ...We are not Demons. We are what Demons fear...

name: Stormcaller's Shock
flavor: ...And so the Druid rose, let out a sad sigh and looked to his fellows. He spoke:...

name: Demon Lord's Tome
flavor: ...If anything, my research shows that they are a race just like Human, Elf, and Orc...

name: Desecrator's Work
flavor: ...But to control it, to manipulate it, to eliminate the weakness that is Life, so that we become Death...

name: Burning Hell Crown
flavor: Hell? What is it but a fictional representation of all things evil?..

name: Burning Hell Robes
flavor: ...I must ask you, Council of Templars, what separates our flames from those of the great and holy Caine?..

name: Burning Hell Scepter
flavor: ...Your beliefs are misguided, dear Council. Frankly, I think they are Heresy. And you will all burn for it.

name: Burning Hell Opus
flavor: ...Are ours not the same bright light of purity? The same cleansing warmth of Life?..

name: Masochist's Helm
flavor: The Council recognizes your importance in recent and past events, and with that in mind, you will live...

name: Masochist's Robes
flavor: ...However we cannot turn a blind eye towards the atrocities you and your disciples have committed...

name: Masochist's Staff
flavor: ...Henceforth you and your disciples are exiled from the Templar Order. The Death Knights are no more.

name: Masochist's Journal
flavor: ...Nor can we ignore the heresy of your actions and beliefs...
